column2: "...So, the fighting did start. Kotoshiro must have foreseen this."
"There's also Darker reactions... this is a fight we're obliged to join!"
"Ahh, ahh, Miko-sama! Miko-sama, please save us Shironians!"
"Those Kuronians have forded the river in unprecedented numbers. How vile! How foolish! Miko-sama, with divine punishment..."
"...Ohh, whatever. Does anyone know where Kotoshiro went? Someone tell me!"
"Keeper Kotoshiro? There is no need for the Keeper, Miko-sama. As long as Miko-sama is here..."
"Yes, if only Miko-sama acts, there will be no problems."
"That's right Miko-sama! Enact divine retribution on those foolish Kuronians!"
"That way of adulating one person so much... I hate that."
"It seemed like he was heading towards the Ash Miko..."
"1章 灰の神子は何処に舞う"
